# Noita RTX

Global illumination lighting overhaul mod for Noita.

This mod is work in progress and there are many missing features from the final release. Version 1.0.0 will be published to the Steam Workshop.

# Install

Download a ready-to-install zip file of the latest stable version from the [releases tab](https://github.com/alex-3141/noita_rtx/releases), and extract that zip file into your game's mod folder.

Make sure the folder path follows the pattern: `Noita\mods\noita_rtx\init.lua`.